  • Classes in eu.smartdatalake.simsearch used by eu.smartdatalake.simsearch 
    Class and Description
    Assistant
    Auxiliary class that provides various helper methods.
    DatasetIdentifier
    Provides identification for the attribute of a given dataset.
    DatasetInfo
    Auxiliary class that provides information about the data sources (each named with their queryable column) available for similarity search operations.
    DataSource
    Instantiates a connection to a data source, either a path to a CSV file or a JDBC connection pool.
    IValueFinder
    Interface for retrieving attribute values for a given object identifier.
    Logger
    Auxiliary class that keeps a log of executed operations.
    PartialResult
    Auxiliary class representing a result from search against a single attribute along with the resulting similarity score.
    SearchResponse
    Provides the complete response to a multi-attribute search query, which encapsulates the search results and their similarity matrix.
